entries.newValue: Cursor is an AI-assisted coding product built by Anysphere. Its mission is to accelerate software development by integrating state-of-the-art language models into a developer-first IDE experience for editing, navigation, refactoring and agentic code generation.

StepFun is a Chinese AI company based in Shanghai. Its mission is to develop large language and multimodal foundation models and make them available for real-world applications across reasoning, agentic workflows and general AI products.

Upstage is a South Korean AI company. Its mission is to improve work productivity by building cost-effective enterprise AI, including large language models (e.g., Solar) and document AI/OCR systems that automate and scale knowledge work.

Voyage is a US AI company focused on retrieval infrastructure. Its mission is to power high-quality search and RAG systems with strong embedding and reranking models that help developers build accurate information retrieval and discovery experiences.
